/posticons/shieldtr.gif" align=absmiddle>  48th Ogre warrior needs help with gear!</span><hr size=1> Ok I'm a warrior on a budget, I have all my crafted still and nothing better but hey I'm at a decent enough AC, I have a thick leather apron (I pine for a fbss) 2 orc fang earrings, nothing on my back yet, and I have a neck slot thats garbage, and a dented brass mask and 2 jagged bands. For my weapons i have a crystal fiber Dmg 8, Dly 26 and a beserkers sword Dmg 12, Dly 36 (Garbage eq I know but it's all I have) And a Runic carver Dmg 18, Dly 37. Now my question is, can you all suggest to a warrior on a budget what and how to go about getting this type of better gear? I'm only got like 200pp and while I'm hoping to start getting in on raids to get planar gear it's going to be awhile probably so lets exclude that. I've been pretty much just leveling over in the DL's and my gear is good enough for that but I'm nearly 49 and I'm hoping that soon I'll be able to go out on the cool raids etc. Thanks  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umoghedancarns.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Moghedan Carns</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.starlance.com/mw4/images/logos/cncnew.gif height=15 width=15 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#CC9900>(8/15/01 4:56:42 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/fashion/Steel_Troll_Male.jpg hieght=74 width=54></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.brellserilis.net/images/posticons/shieldtr.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: 48th Ogre warrior needs help with gear!</span><hr size=1> go to everfrost, sneak by brandl (single guard, south entrance to plains) find martar icebear (or Karg ) and kill him... very very easy.  <br>
